data.title: FiOS technology overview and QAM Video scan results
data.meta_description: Background For the past five years we've been Verizon FiOS customers. They're the only wired MSO that we have to choose from, though there is CLEC fiber on our street that I've asked (unsuccessfully so far) about getting service on. We're generally happy with our service, despite lack of IPv6 â¦
